sequenceDiagram
    participant Startup as 启动流程
    participant Manager as PluginInstallationManager
    participant Reconciler as reconcileMarketplaces
    participant AppState

    Startup->>Manager: performBackgroundPluginInstallations(setAppState)
    Manager->>Reconciler: diffMarketplaces(declared, materialized)
    Reconciler-->>Manager: diff（missing + sourceChanged）
    Manager->>AppState: setAppState（批量设置 pending 状态）

    loop 安装事件流
        Reconciler->>Manager: onProgress({type: 'installing', name})
        Manager->>AppState: updateMarketplaceStatus(installing)
        Reconciler->>Manager: onProgress({type: 'installed', name})
        Manager->>AppState: updateMarketplaceStatus(installed)
    end

    alt 有新安装
        Manager->>AppState: refreshActivePlugins（清除缓存，重建连接）
    else 仅更新
        Manager->>AppState: needsRefresh = true（通知用户手动刷新）
    end
